      "label": "Legend",
      "position": {
        "x": -760,
        "y": 20
      },
      "width": 320,
      "height": 180,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Legend\n- bridge cluster: local creation vocabulary for planning and agent classes\n- run anchor: `task`\n- actor: `agent`\n- boundary: `contract`\n- instruction: `prompt`\n- capability: `tool`\n- evidence: `observation`\n- output: `result`\n- transfer: `handoff`\n- unresolved: `open-question`"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "agent-prompting-template-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Agent Prompting Template",
      "position": {
        "x": -80,
        "y": -120
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "ports": [
        {
          "id": "root",
          "label": "root",
          "direction": "bidirectional",
          "dataType": "any",
          "position": {
            "side": "right",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Agent Prompting Template\n\nThis is the canonical working template for a bounded agent run.\n\nMinimum contract:\n- a run has a `task` anchor\n- a bounded `agent`\n- an explicit `contract`\n- an authored `prompt`\n- a declared `tool` when capability use is involved\n- at least one `observation`\n- a visible `result`\n- and an explicit `handoff` when responsibility moves onward\n\nThe bridge rows are the authoritative class surfaces for this template.",
        "isRoot": true,
        "root": true,
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
